Saturday s sponsored golf day provided an opportunity for 79 golfers to enjoy a round of golf at the Polokwane Golf Club. The game was in Better Ball format and the winners were Ignis Mar and Marcel Meyer with 55 points. Phil Masekane and Francois Hartlief ended second with 49 points. Ignis Mar , Phil Masekane, Jacques Pretorius, Jacques Scheepers, Leon Zietsman, Roelf de Beer and Martin van Ghent each won R50 in the Two Clubs. Story and photos: BARRY VILJOEN &gt;&gt;barryv.observer@gmail.com Andries du Plessis takes a swing on the 9th. Charles Mara lines up for the hole. Joe Mackays and Francois Hartlief enjoy a light lunch after their round of golf.